- Report covers 5 phases: BRCA classification (99 deficient/2119 total), HR validation (0/8 FDR-sig but directionally correct), genome-wide screen (3,709 novel non-HR genes), PRISM drugs (PARPi absent, afuresertib AKTi found), TCGA integration (~45,223 patients/yr)
